<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Email Confirmation - Real Estate App</title>
    <style>
      @import url("https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Outfit:wght@200;300;400;500;700&display=swap");

      * {
        font-family: "Outfit";
        font-size: 20px;
      }
      .logo-wrap {
        text-align: center;
        padding: 2em;
      }
    </style>
  </head>

  <body style="margin: 0; padding: 0; background-color: #f4f4f4">
    <div style="text-align: center; padding: 20px">
      <div class="logo-wrap">
        <h1 style="color: #4a8fc3; margin: 0;">  Real Estate App</h1>
      </div>
      <h2 style="color: #272727; margin-bottom: 1em;">Welcome to Real Estate App!</h2>
      <p style="margin: 0; color: #272727; margin-bottom: 3em">
        We're excited to have you get started. First, you need to confirm your
        account. Just press the button below.
      </p>
      <a
        href="<%= newPath %>"
        target="_blank"
        style="
          font-size: 20px;
          color: #ffffff;
          text-decoration: none;
          padding: 15px 25px;
          border-radius: 8px;
          background-color: #4a8fc3;
          display: inline-block;
          margin: 20px 0;
        "
        >Confirm Your Email</a
      >
      <p style="margin: 20px 0; color: #666666">
        If you have any questions, just reply to this email, we're always happy
        to help out.
      </p>
      <p style="margin: 0; color: #666666">Cheers,<br />Real Estate Team</p>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
  </body>
</html>
